# FBX source files are kept locally for re-conversion / editing in
# Blender, but the deployed asset is the .glb variant (converted via
# `FBX2glTF --binary`, roughly 59% smaller). Regenerate any missing
# FBX from Mixamo → export FBX (with skin), then re-run FBX2glTF.
*.fbx
# Texture caches created by FBX2glTF during conversion — safe to delete.
*.fbm/
